data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_3a80381a9aa9e0d30069a28ae07d008190a820f40f21c153c2","logprobs":[],"output_index":2,"sequence_number":352,"text":"Based on the available Contoso documentation, there is currently **one Contoso product described**:\n\n## Contoso SmartView Glasses (Contoso Galaxy Innovations)\n**Category:** Smart Eyewear \n\n### Key features\n- **Augmented Reality (AR) interface** for overlaying digital content in your field of view   \n- **Voice-controlled AI agent** for hands-free control and assistance   \n- **HD video recording with 3D audio** to capture immersive video and sound   \n- **UV protection + blue light filtering** to help protect eyes during outdoor use and screen/AR viewing   \n- **Wireless charging with extended battery life** for easier charging and longer use between charges   \n\n### Included documentation topics (what the user guide covers)\nThe documentation also outlines what’s in the user guide for setup and ongoing use, including:\n- Product introduction and overview\n- Sizing/fit guidance\n- Care/maintenance instructions\n- Break-in period (adjusting to AR use)\n- Safety tips (public/private spaces)\n- Troubleshooting quick fixes   \n\n### Warranty, support, and returns\n- **Warranty:** Two-year limited warranty on electronic components   \n- **Support contact:** support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com   \n- **Return policy:** 30-day return, “no questions asked”   \n- **FAQ topics:** syncing with devices, connection troubleshooting, AR environment customization   \n\nIf you have additional Contoso docs (e.g., more product pages, a catalog, or separate manuals) and upload them, I can expand this into a full product lineup comparison."}

